Global Ultrasonic Debridement Knife Market Insights
Ultrasonic Debridement Knife Market size was valued at USD 0.35 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.65 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Ultrasonic Debridement Knife Market Overview
The global ultrasonic debridement market was valued at $135.4 million in 2022 and is projected to reach $240.6 million by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.43% from 2023 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for advanced wound care solutions that promote healing and enhance patient comfort.

